            <title>[LU-12169] Assertion on mdc_pack_name</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-12169</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt; If some race happen, dentry name which we copied is invalid,&lt;br/&gt;
 we should return failure directly rather than continue.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt; Because Server doesn&apos;t support open-by-fid, we pass @name&lt;br/&gt;
 as NULL, @len as 0, it will definitely trigger following&lt;br/&gt;
 assertion in mdc_pack_name()&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;  LustreError: 157839:0:(mdc_lib.c:137:mdc_pack_name()) LBUG&lt;/p&gt;</description>
